This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the semantics of natural language. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as these fields often use vector models for language processing. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as these fields also deal with the logical aspects of language.
